==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overpress
<hw>O`ver*press"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
bear upon with irresistible force; to crush; to overwhelm.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To overcome by importunity.</def>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overpressure</ent>⟦br⟧
